This is the TODO list for phpLdapPasswd.

* Allow configuring anonymous / non-anonmyous binding to LDAP directory
  * See bind_anonymously()
* Allow configuration of From/Reply-To heading in fatal error messages.
* Fix fatal_error function so it properly parses template.  (Right now, it
  prints the error message regardless of if the template asks for it.)
* Secure configuration file, (e.g. put outside of web root).
* Allow for custom help links for the input fields.
* Create a search function that can take certain input information and return
  a user ID, (e.g. for forgotten IDs).
* Update documentation.
* Put change last date in own function.
* Combine email and form special tags, and add a tag for SYSADMINEMAIL.
